.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.pytest_cache
.ruff_cache
# A developer's leftover local stamp (from `just build`, before its cleanup trap) must never be
# copied by `COPY . .` and baked stale; the build-arg path is the authoritative source (ADR-0370).
src/kdive/_buildinfo.py
**/node_modules
tests
docs
deploy
.github
# Do NOT exclude *.md at the root: pyproject declares `readme = "README.md"`, which the
# uv_build backend reads during `uv sync` — excluding it breaks the project install.
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
